{"tid":99522,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"唉，過年同班同學拜年，一講樓，即刻灰哂。。","createTime":"2017-01-29T09:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T06:59:06.000Z","uid":51615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd3eb603e28f06fdfe4e0373398198f9e77bb3d","tid":99522,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"班中同，大同，十個有八個都上哂車，拜年一坐埋一齊，班既得利益者就話唔係升一百五十萬就係升左一百萬，個個都好似發左達咁，用層樓來撻人，席間得我同另一個仲租緊樓住，係度睇住班人不可一世既樣，好撚sad<br />\n<br />\n明明當年大家都柒下柒下，畢左業都係五六年姐，買到樓既就係到睇唔起人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1886d9194bebf4f85a952fc2a59110a5115aaf","tid":99522,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"講下班人買左邊，有；<br />\n<br />\n將中<br />\n得寶<br />\n德褔<br />\n荃威<br />\n新葵芳<br />\n愉城<br />\n栢麗灣<br />\n<br />\n最勁果個逼海籃天<br />\n<br />\n而我租緊屯門井財單幢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4215ad8646ac5f64d8d7ac754068656496de0a","tid":99522,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:27:10.000Z","msg":"巴打中學名校，全部都有家底？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35afb49b4a005ff694291afd48adb40f2d240ff","tid":99522,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打中學名校，全部都有家底？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梁球居。。<br />\n<br />\n據我所知，全部都係靠自己"},{"pid":"0b81fa5932accc29c3e7e046d4717cc1a3ebb7b0","tid":99522,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打中學名校，全部都有家底？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梁球居。。<br />\n<br />\n據我所知，全部都係靠自己</blockquote><br />\n幾歲到？30？"},{"pid":"4baf5d3847f2d18ee3d07a358bcf21c5a86633cb","tid":99522,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T09:36